## ðŸ“¢ Key Insights

- Resort hotels generate more seasonal revenue, with peaks in summer.
- Cancellations significantly reduce actual revenue, especially from long lead-time bookings.
- Bookings from specific countries contribute disproportionately to total earnings.
- Forecasting suggests a potential 12-15% increase in revenue in the next high season.

